quran[17]{c,v,t}:
  23,43,"Mofte woo lajal majje ngal adotaako …óe, …ďe nennantaake kadi"
  23,44,"Refti Men Nuli Nulaa…ďe Amen …ďen ko …ďe jokkondir…ďe, tuma kala ari e mofte Nulaa…óo majje on …ďe fenna mo Men jokkini yoga e ma…ď…ďe yoga, Men wa…ói …ďe yewtereeji, wo…ó…óineede wonanii yim…ďe …ďe gom…óintaa …ďen"
  23,45,Refti Men Nuli Muusaa e musi…ó…óo makko on Haaruuna wonndude e Aayeeje Amen …óen e hujja …ďanngu…óo
  23,46,"Faade e Fir'awna e mbatu mu'un ngun, …ďe mawnintinii …ďe laatii yim…ďe townitii…ďe"
  23,47,"∆Āe wi'i: \"Enee, hara men gom…óinayyim…ďe …ói…óo yeru amen, hara yim…ďe ma…ď…ďe ko maccu…ďe amen"
  23,48,"∆Āe fenni …ďen …ói…óo, …ďe laatii jeyaa…ďe e halkaa…ďe …ďen"
  23,49,Gom…óii Men Okkiino Muusaa Deftere nden belejo'o kam…ďe …ďe feewa
  23,50,"Men wa…ói ge…óal Mariyama on e neene makko Maande, Men werni …ďe faade e tulde joomiraare √Īi…ďrude e callungol"
  23,51,"Ko onon yo Nulaa…ďe, √Īaamee immorde e laa…ďu…ói …óin gollon ko mo∆ī∆īi, pellet Min, Mi…óo Anndi ko golloton kon"
  23,52,"E pellet, kaa Diina mo'on ko Diina woota, ko Min woni Joomi mo'on hulee Lam"
  23,53,"∆Āe ta∆īi fiyaake ma…ď…ďe on hakkunde ma…ď…ďe dente, kala fedde no farnora ko woni kon ka mayre"
  23,54,∆äalu …ďe e siwrere nden haa e dummunne
  23,55,"Enee, hara …ďe sikku wonndema ko Men …ďeydiri …ďe kon immorde e jawdi e …ďi…ó…ďe"
  23,56,"Men yaccinanay …ďe e mo∆ī∆īereeji, ko woni …ďe so'aa"
  23,57,"Pellet, …ďen …ďe ka√Īum immorde e kulol Joomi ma…ď…ďe hara ko …ďe hulu…ďe"
  23,58,E …ďen …ďe ka√Īum ko …ďe gom…óin…ďe Aayeeje Joomi ma…ď…ďe …óen
  23,59,E …ďen …ďe ka√Īum …ďe wonah sirkanoo…ďe Joomi ma…ď…ďe
